@TradexWhisperer Now that everyone knows where this is going. I think we will have to find ourselves a new play by Q3 / Q4. 

Is it CPO / optics / photonics? Perhaps, but with these valuations there’s only a couple of firms that are not priced for perfection yet.

What’s your view?

